          <p>Yes. For urgent appointments, we offer rush service with same-day completion. Provide your appointment time and we prioritize accordingly. For best results, submit documents by morning for afternoon/evening appointments. We have couriers available for physical delivery within Dubai.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
